===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|nautical}} A [[sail]] or either of the two sails rigged just above the [[course sail]] and supported by the topmast on a square-rigged sailing ship.
# {{lb|en|nautical}} In a [[fore-and-aft]]-rigged sailing boat, the sail that is set above the [[gaff]] at the top part of the mast.

